  m_Name: Glimpse_of_Fate
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::AbilitySO
  abilityName: Glimpse of Fate
  description: "Once per day you can undo a single action\nperformed by you or your
    Company, declaring\nit was in fact a minor vision you received.\nPlay as if it
    never happened.\nPASSION - Respect\nRestore SPI when you yield to a Seer.\nThe
    blood sees through time aflow\nTo certain souls, a glimpse they show\nGazer Knight\nTAPESTRY
    STORY\nEvent Subject\n1 Birth of... A random Seer\n2 Great deeds of... A random
    Knight\n3 Ambitions of... Yourself\n4 Shameful death of... One of the Company\n5
    Glorious death of... The Realm ruler\n6 Peaceful death of... An unknown figure\nKNIGHTED
    BY...\nThe Stone Seer\n6GD, A3, treat as a Structure\n\u2022 A 10ft statue dragged
    from the earth,\nmotionless and silent. Never moves or\nresponds, but those who
    speak with him\nget a general feel of approval or objection.\n\u2022 Knows all
    of the past but nothing of the\nfuture or present.\n\u2022 Wants to preserve
    the Realm.\nPerson: Furious outcast ~ Name: Gil ~ Characteristic: Muscular slab\nObject:
    Mossy drum ~ Beast: Dark swan ~ State: Arguing ~ Theme: Size\n4\n5\nThe"
